    "• We recommend that future studies should consider exploring the use of neural topic (BERT embeddings) models to enhance recommender systems.",
    "This is because the neural topic models have produced state-of-the-art results in the TM field.",
    "• We establish that the co-occurrence maps which uses clustering analysis produces relatedness of publications based on citation relations can be enhanced using TM, another statistical tool which is useful to extend the co-occurrence analyses by uncovering hidden themes.",
    "Thus, our study recommends that bibliometrics community should incorporate TM to better understand research themes.",
    "Especially in the era of open data sources and full text databases."
